<br>
2.  invite stage = person who has been approved to come to raids, is not guilded unless during a raid.<br>
<br>
3.  sponser stage = person has found 3 people willing to sponser, is not a member, but is guilded.<br>
<br>
4.  member stage = someone who has passed a 30day sponsership and received 75%+ Yes votes with zero No votes during that time.<br>
<br>
Person must be guildless before they can send in an application to start stage #1.  Like I mentioned before, you gotta burn all your bridges before you even know if you can attend a single raid.  Most people who like to guildjump to get loot don't have the balls to make that sort of blind leap.<br>
<br>
